# Candidates

A candidate is defined by a unqiue email adress. If a candidate don't have any <code>job_applications</code> it can be either <code>sourced</code> or <code>connected</code>

When <code>sourced</code> the candidate was added to the system by a recruiter.

A candidate that is <code>connected</code> has opted in to recieve new job notifications and has also the option to create a richer and more personal profile.

